graph TB
    subgraph "Feast Operator Component"
        Operator[Feast Operator<br/>Go Kubernetes Operator]
        LeaderElection[Leader Election]
        Operator -->|manages| LeaderElection
    end

    subgraph "Feature Store Services"
        OnlineStore[Online Feature Store<br/>Python Service<br/>6566/6567 TCP]
        OfflineStore[Offline Feature Store<br/>Python Service<br/>8815/8816 TCP]
        Registry[Registry Server<br/>Python Service gRPC/REST<br/>6570/6571 TCP]
        UI[UI Server<br/>Python Service Optional<br/>8888/8443 TCP]
        CronJob[CronJob<br/>Materialization Tasks]
    end

    subgraph "Storage Backends"
        SQLite[(SQLite<br/>Default)]
        PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL<br/>Production)]
        Redis[(Redis<br/>Low-latency)]
        S3[(S3/GCS/Azure<br/>Object Storage)]
        Snowflake[(Snowflake<br/>Data Warehouse)]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        FeatureStoreCR[FeatureStore CR<br/>feast.dev/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| FeatureStoreCR
    FeatureStoreCR -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|deploys| OnlineStore
    Operator -->|deploys| OfflineStore
    Operator -->|deploys| Registry
    Operator -->|deploys| UI
    Operator -->|creates| CronJob

    OnlineStore -->|reads/writes| SQLite
    OnlineStore -->|reads/writes| PostgreSQL
    OnlineStore -->|reads/writes| Redis
    OnlineStore -->|queries metadata| Registry

    OfflineStore -->|reads historical data| S3
    OfflineStore -->|queries| PostgreSQL
    OfflineStore -->|queries| Snowflake
    OfflineStore -->|queries metadata| Registry

    Registry -->|stores metadata| PostgreSQL
    Registry -->|stores metadata| S3

    CronJob -->|materializes features| OnlineStore
    CronJob -->|fetches data from| OfflineStore

    UI -->|displays| Registry

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
        ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Optional]
        OIDC[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Optional]
    end

    Operator -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    Operator -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    Operator -->|integrates| ODHDashboard
    Operator -->|requests certs| CertManager
    OnlineStore -.->|auth| OIDC
    OfflineStore -.->|auth| OIDC
    Registry -.->|auth| OIDC
    UI -.->|auth| OIDC

